                     <interp inst="t18290409-99-person1009" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was going by and took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was looking at the trousers - I fell in at the threshold of the door; I was going to pick them up - he came, took hold of me, and struck me.</p>

               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290409-99-person1010">
